name: Blair
tweet: It’s so unfair to give De Gea stick for the points we dropped recently. Firstly, United bottled it as a team. Secondly, players make mistakes! What we should be worried about is that we are unable to recover from the individual mistakes.

tweet: It’s beyond me how United letting Herrera go and keeping players like Young, Jones, and Smalling.

name: Blair
tweet: Sacking Jose or selling mediocre players won’t solve the actual issue. To solve all the mess United have, we should get rid of the Glazers and Woodward. Realistically, that’s impossible. So here we are, the fans, have to suffer from it for how long we don’t know. Ffs.
